  "2153430": {
    "name": "信号迷局 Signal Maze",
    "steam_appid": 2153430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/1fa8fce2a8e3aa649c1e06cef9e4f91a.avif?t=1743995898\" width=500 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《信号迷局》这款游戏中，您可以游玩到这一部被称为 R.O.O.T. 的系统。它的运作基于一个个单元的排列组合。你将操作单元在操作面板上移动。单元会产生、传递信号；单元与单元也由信号连接、激活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎉历经了一年半的 Steam 抢先体验模式和多次更新后，解谜游戏《信号迷局》（原名 R.O.O.T）终于在 2025 年 1 月 16 日正式发售！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨完整版包含全部 150 个关卡，并为主要关卡（约30关）新增了美式漫画风格的内容，带来沉浸感十足的故事体验。以及更新了23个，现在共有33个成就供您挑战！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩同时，游戏还加入了多种全新玩法机制，并完成了大量的 Bug 修复与程序优化，为玩家提供更流畅、更丰富的解谜乐趣。感谢你的耐心等待，现在就来开启这场全新的解谜之旅吧！💡  <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/f105fb306afd026c3ed346edb6e0eb02.poster.avif?t=1743995898\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/f105fb306afd026c3ed346edb6e0eb02.webm?t=1743995898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/f105fb306afd026c3ed346edb6e0eb02.mp4?t=1743995898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是别忘了，时间也不是无穷无尽的；虽然这个“时间”可能和你想象的不太一样。在R.O.O.T.中，你有无限量的客观时间来考虑每一步，你真正有限的就是“步数”。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就这样，一个个单元就通过信号连接成一条条链路；这些链路中的信号又反过来激活了更多的单元。激活的单元又会产生一笔笔收入，目的达到！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/25138f7873aec22eeb7cc733cce4ec88.poster.avif?t=1743995898\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/25138f7873aec22eeb7cc733cce4ec88.webm?t=1743995898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/25138f7873aec22eeb7cc733cce4ec88.mp4?t=1743995898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以将这些收入攒起来完成任务；也可以用它们购买更多的单元，来扩大你的生产。你要怎么做？都听你的！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不怕你不赚钱，就怕你不敢赚钱。人有多大胆，单元就有多大产。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/7ad4851a94f79f0da03c36b4fa8cc217.poster.avif?t=1743995898\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/7ad4851a94f79f0da03c36b4fa8cc217.webm?t=1743995898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/7ad4851a94f79f0da03c36b4fa8cc217.mp4?t=1743995898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除此以外，您还可以体验到：主角博特“入职”雷文钛科公司，成为远端计算部的一名新员工，然后和这家公司斗智斗勇的故事。博特的工作内容就是操作R.O.O.T.系统上的单元，通过排列组合帮助公司获得收益，完成公司定下的KPI目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/702698bf71e2b894c8417e9e8e1e44f9.avif?t=1743995898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras_big/702698bf71e2b894c8417e9e8e1e44f9.avif?t=1743995898 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是在这百无聊赖的公司的工作生活中，善于观察的博特发现公司的一些公共设施有一些异常的表现，什么？似乎是在食堂？在好奇心的驱使下，博特与他的黑客好友埃斯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras/1853346a62d3f4fdd16974fc5636b128.avif?t=1743995898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153430/extras_big/1853346a62d3f4fdd16974fc5636b128.avif?t=1743995898 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这两位年轻人，无论是出于好奇，还是想赚点儿外快，开始一同调查公司背后隐藏的秘密。他们的行动会顺利嘛？他们的结局会是怎样的？恐怕不会是一帆风顺的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论如何，我们邀请您一起和博特开启在雷文钛科跌宕起伏的故事和精心设计的解谜关卡吧！</p>",
